'''涎腺玻璃样变透明细胞癌'''（Hyalinizing clear cell carcinoma，HCCC）是一种罕见的[[恶性|恶性]][[唾腺|唾液腺]][[贅生物|肿瘤]]，预后良好，通常见于[[舌|舌头]]或[[腭|上颚]]。<ref name="pmid21669357">{{Cite journal|title=Hyalinizing clear cell carcinoma: a case report and review of the literature|last=Kauzman|first=A.|last2=Tabet|first2=JC.|date=Jul 2011|journal=Oral Surg Oral Med Oral Pathol Oral Radiol Endod|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.tripleo.2011.02.041|volume=112|pages=e26–34|pmid=21669357|last3=Stiharu|first3=TI.}}</ref>

== 症状 ==
HCCC通常存在于[[口腔|口腔]]中，无痛。<ref name="pmid7506496">{{Cite journal|title=Hyalinizing clear cell carcinoma of salivary gland|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-surgical-pathology_1994-01_18_1/page/74|last=Milchgrub|first=S.|last2=Gnepp|first2=DR.|date=Jan 1994|journal=Am J Surg Pathol|issue=1|doi=10.1097/00000478-199401000-00007|volume=18|pages=74–82|pmid=7506496|last3=Vuitch|first3=F.|last4=Delgado|first4=R.|last5=Albores-Saavedra|first5=J.}}</ref>

== 诊断 ==
HCCC通过组织检查（例如[[活體組織切片|活體組織切片]]）来诊断。

=== 病理 ===
HCCC由具有丰富透明[[細胞質|细胞质]]的细胞组成，呈索状、小梁状或簇状排列于透明基质中。<ref name="pmid20596970">{{Cite journal|title=Hyalinizing clear cell carcinoma: report of eight cases and a review of literature|last=O'Sullivan-Mejia|first=ED.|last2=Massey|first2=HD.|date=Sep 2009|journal=Head Neck Pathol|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s12105-009-0124-3|volume=3|pages=179–85|pmc=2811632|pmid=20596970|last3=Faquin|first3=WC.|last4=Powers|first4=CN.}}</ref>核多形性通常很小，少见[[有絲分裂|有丝分裂]]。<ref name="pmid7506496">{{Cite journal|title=Hyalinizing clear cell carcinoma of salivary gland|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-surgical-pathology_1994-01_18_1/page/74|last=Milchgrub|first=S.|last2=Gnepp|first2=DR.|date=Jan 1994|journal=Am J Surg Pathol|issue=1|doi=10.1097/00000478-199401000-00007|volume=18|pages=74–82|pmid=7506496|last3=Vuitch|first3=F.|last4=Delgado|first4=R.|last5=Albores-Saavedra|first5=J.}}</ref>

由于肿瘤细胞的[[糖原|糖原]]含量，其在[[顯微鏡|显微镜]]下外观清晰，可被[[PAS染色法|PAS染色]]。[[S100蛋白|S100]]和[[平滑肌肌动蛋白|平滑肌肌动蛋白]]（SMA）的[[免疫染色|免疫染色]]通常为阴性，而[[细胞角蛋白|细胞角蛋白]]和[[上皮膜抗原|上皮膜抗原]]（EMA）则为阳性。

HCCC通常具有复发性[[染色體易位|染色体易位]]t(12;22)，涉及基因[[EWSR1|EWSR1]]和[[ATF1|ATF1]]。<ref name="pmid21484932">{{Cite journal|title=EWSR1-ATF1 fusion is a novel and consistent finding in hyalinizing clear-cell carcinoma of salivary gland|last=Antonescu|first=CR.|last2=Katabi|first2=N.|date=Jul 2011|journal=Genes Chromosomes Cancer|issue=7|doi=10.1002/gcc.20881|volume=50|pages=559–70|pmid=21484932|last3=Zhang|first3=L.|last4=Sung|first4=YS.|last5=Seethala|first5=RR.|last6=Jordan|first6=RC.|last7=Perez-Ordoñez|first7=B.|last8=Have|first8=C.|last9=Asa|first9=SL.|display-authors=8}}</ref>在[[透明细胞肉瘤|透明细胞肉瘤]]中可见相同的易位。

[[组织学|组织学]][[鑑別診斷|鉴别诊断]]包括[[粘液表皮样癌|粘液表皮样癌]]（透明细胞变体）、[[腺泡细胞癌|腺泡细胞癌]]（透明细胞变体）、[[上皮-肌上皮癌|上皮-肌上皮癌]]和转移性[[透明细胞癌|透明细胞癌]]。

== 预后 ==
HCCC通常预后良好。<ref name="pmid21393908">{{Cite journal|title=Hyalinizing clear cell carcinoma of the base of tongue: a distinct and rare entity|last=Masilamani|first=S.|last2=Rao|first2=S.|journal=Indian J Pathol Microbiol|issue=1|doi=10.4103/0377-4929.77393|year=2011|volume=54|pages=167–9|pmid=21393908|last3=Chirakkal|first3=P.|last4=Kumar|first4=AR.|subscription=free}}</ref>

